column5: I figured some of you may enjoy this interesting footage.  Trip of a lifetime! Many thanks to Jet for inviting us out and being a great guide.  GoPro was only used for 2 days out of the entire trip, but got quite a bit of footage. I'll work on uploading the rest later.  Note: audio is very low due to sealed waterproof case, but there is some swearing.
Thanks for sharing! The background/scenery is absolutely stunning!
can never get withdrawls with footage like this...Nice Job!
Oh the memories . . . . over much too soon.

You should've tested how waterproof the GoPro was without the housing  Definitely the most awesome trip I've ever been on. A couple days ago I watched a few of the vids we took and realized that a good portion of them were of us losing fish.LOL
sweet vid.   i'm working in central bc right now.  it's a beautiful province and i never get sick of the mountains!
Trip of a lifetime indeed.   I don't think I will ever feel more devastated from losing a fish lol
